<h3>1</h3>
  <p>Find <code>&lt;div id="screen" class="bg-primary"&gt;</code>. Hint: it's a child node of <code>&lt;body&gt;</code>.</p>
  <p>Find the rule for <code>#screen</code>.
  <p>Change its <code>background-color</code> style. Try the color palete. Try manually entering colour values <code>#00F</code>, <code>white</code>, <code>transparent</code>.</p>

